Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:04.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pale broken wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:12.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are just a bit tired from\Nthat clear blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:17.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to force\Nyour smiles for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:24.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now... to smile for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Loneliness still continues to stalk me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:32.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A candle lit within
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:36.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The party is lively;\Nthe chandeliers are gorgeous, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:43.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I fill the hole left behind\Nby those lacking words?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:46.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:53.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can at least swim freely\Nin my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:56.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't need a sky like that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:01:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can face tomorrow without painting\Nover all the things up to yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:10.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pale broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:17.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are just a bit tired from\Nthat clear blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:22.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to force\Nyour smiles for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:29.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now... to smile for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:31.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:34.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the spiritual guardians\Nof the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:37.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the balancers who\Nkeep a close eye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:40.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on the countless souls,\Ngood and evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that fill this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:48.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and Toshiro's advance\Ntroops barely defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Arrancar that Aizen had created,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but both sides suffer\Na lot of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:02:02.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerned that they cannot defeat\Nthe stronger Arrancars as they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:06.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Soul Reapers all decide to\Nprepare themselves after the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:15.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uryu and Sado also begin training\Nto become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Ichigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:25.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,sensing that he cannot\Nsuppress his inner Hollow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:28.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,visits the Visored.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you knew\Nwhere we were...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:42.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:51.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your coming here means that\Nyou've decided to join us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:56.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:01.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to take advantage\Nof you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't join you guys, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to show me how to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...suppress the Hollow inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your barrier all right, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:54.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!\NYou still don't understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you not\Nto be scared, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you something useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:05.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:07.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:08.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that if you\Nuse your Bankai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,against someone as\Npowerful as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:15.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you're suddenly going to lose\Ncontrol of your inner Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scared, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:18.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "Shut up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:20.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Baldy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I get annoyed when I look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep getting nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:27.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hate this so much,\Nthen do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to use your Bankai\Nor turn into a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just finish you off...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:46.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she become a Hollow\Nand still remain conscious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she put on and\Ntake off that mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:54.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fighting her in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can watch her as much\Nas I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:58.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I watch her and think about it,\NI should understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't use my Bankai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:05.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't turn into a Hollow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't open up\Nmy soul to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:06.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any complaints,\Ndo you, Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand now don't you, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:18.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Hollow can't be suppressed\Njust by thinking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:21.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with your mind and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to pound knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:35.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of how to suppress your Hollow all\Nthe way into the heart of your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:41.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,KUROSAKI CLINIC
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:46.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo's not coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up... It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come wandering back after\Ntwo or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so calm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be a kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:06:59.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A crime's been committed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!\NWhat's wrong, Yuzu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just wait a second, Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:11.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show you\Nmy killer one-shot gag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:14.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I do this, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mustachioed man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were always\Na mustachioed man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:40.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:41.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:57.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even sense any trace\Nof his Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:18.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk... Don't make this kid cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a hopeless big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:36.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch is late...\NHiyori, make something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to\Nmake something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did, I wouldn't let\Nyou eat it, baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:49.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Love, did you hear\NPrince of Darkness's new song
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that just came out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:55.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Rose, did you read\Nthis week's Jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:56.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:59.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- You never let me read it anyway.\N- This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:05.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa, make sure you look\Nafter that Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:07.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not watching him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just looking at\Nswimsuit models!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interrupt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:16.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on duty today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to shout out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:20.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- One, two!\N- Lunch sure is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- One, two!\N- Baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:30.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:44.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slap you around if\Nyou act stupid, baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:49.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's my line...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd like to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bragged about\Nhow you were going to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,pound in the knowledge of\Nhow to suppress the Hollow within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do I have to row\Nfor more than a day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on this clearly handmade,\Nbeat up, silly machine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:03.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:07.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, am I stupid for rowing\Non it like you told me to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:12.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You're stupid!\NYou're the only stupid one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- And you're bald!\N- We're back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ah, thank you!\N- We finished training,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:18.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so stop blabbing\Nand listen to us, baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up with the "baldy," fangs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.48,0:10:22.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you consider\Nthis training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:25.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think I'm talking\Nabout your hair, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm saying you're wearing a bald wig!\N- I bought you lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Also, my fangs are\N- Do you want to eat it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- my most attractive feature, baldy!\N- Ah! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You called me baldy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Berry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fuming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:35.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:40.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like he doesn't like\Nthe Super Hiyori Trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Only now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:51.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that Hiyori explained\Nthe trainer very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She always says one\Nor two things too little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:14.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain.\NRow until you collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:22.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Silly Hiyori Trainer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:26.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Super!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:28.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the foundation of your future training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:29.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Foundation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:33.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The level of your training\Nis determined
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by how long you can row\Non that machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "level"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as Hiyori says.\NDon't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep rowing on the Silly Hiyori Trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to make you\Nsay it, baldy Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hurt you, baldy Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll teach you how to control\Nyour Hollow transformation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When you are able to row\Non that machine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for at least three days straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:04.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bound to row on this thing\Nfor three days or even a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell after rowing on it all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A person expends an incredible\Namount of spirit energy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,just by touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it's made to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your plan is to see how many days\Nit'll take for me to collapse,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can measure my maximum\Nspirit energy capacity, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But with my current spirit energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely go for at least five days!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in measuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me how to control\Nmy Hollow transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:33.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:37.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to be playing around\Nwith you Visored!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:52.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's surprising, coming from\Nsomeone who doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,about the Hogyoku's awakening time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:01.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, stop blabbing when\Nyou don't really know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:07.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,about the Hogyoku or\Nabout Hollow transformations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:13.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? How do you know\Nabout the Hogyoku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:21.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We know about the Hogyoku,\Nthe Arrancars, and Sosuke Aizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:26.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've known all about them\Nfor many, many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the details another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I should take my time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:41.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and get your soul prepared our way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:49.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You became a Soul Reaper,\Ngot your Shikai,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:53.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and got your Bankai\Nat incredible speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:57.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As you say, it might be better for you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if we just teach you how to\Ntransform into a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't regret it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi, build a double barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you are going to undergo\Na complete Hollow transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get eaten! Consume it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get eaten up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:18.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi, place a barrier here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not cute when\Nan old man says it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:26.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Place seals all over Ichigo's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:31.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:41.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wall of iron sand, monk-like tower,\Nthe shimmer of burning iron,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:44.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,unmoving and silent until the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo 75!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gochu Tekkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:31.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while... King...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:38.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty gloomy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is old man Zangetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk about Zangetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,are you talking about\Nthe one that you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...is it the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A white Zangetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:22.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me where\NZangetsu was, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:47.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:55.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, shouldn't we hide\Nhis zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:57.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There wouldn't be any point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That would just make him\Nmore frantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachigen, open this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on duty today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:33.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Only if I don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lisa Yadomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:06.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:20.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! What did you do\Nto old man Zangetsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:23.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How persistent!\NDon't make me keep saying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:39.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo... I'm not sure if you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:43.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but Zangetsu and I...\Nere one to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:47.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Zangetsu and I are your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:51.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a part of Zangetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we all share\Na single body,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:02.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,outlooks change depending\Non who's in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If life is in control, you have flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If death is in control,\Nyou become bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:16.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My power has increased,\Ncontrol has switched over to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:19.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and Zangetsu has become a part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:25.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you try to draw\Nout Zangetsu's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:29.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the easier it's become to\Ncontrol your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:34.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:40.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means that\Nif I defeat you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:44.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,old man Zangetsu will become\Nthe center of my power once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:49.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me it's impossible\Nafter seeing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:12.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:44.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ban...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:45.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...kai!\N- ...kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:54.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I dressed up my five fingers\Nwith a manicure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:22:00.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And then what's glowing\Nwas me instead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:03.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspiration is like a goldfish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:06.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps a voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:09.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sound that\Ndoesn't bounce back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:25.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those lines stretching parallel\Nto each other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:31.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They say one line turns beautiful,\Nthen deteriorate repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:36.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standing right there, \Nbut the way is locked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance grows, \Nbut it's within reach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:41.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And even today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:51.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I trace your gibberish roman letters\Nover and over with my left hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:23:01.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you see the moment\Nyou open your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:11.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What color will\Nhe paint your nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:23.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You there in front of\Nthe TV lacking exercise!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:25.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Super Hiyori Trainer that\NIchigo was using
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,can be yours for a low, low price!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.91,0:23:28.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:30.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and you can get it signed\Nby Hiyori Sarugaki, the Bleach heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:33.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that fraud in two different ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:34.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:37.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!\NGolden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:40.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold my breath! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kon!\N- That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:45.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Give me back my gigai!\N- That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:47.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's my perfect body!\N- Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:49.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- If I trade places with him now,\N- Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.42,0:23:50.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,all my woes will be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:52.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanataro! Toss that over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:54.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:59.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,EXTRACTION PRINCESS\N\N	  \N	  \N	All right, now!\N	May misfortune be upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:04.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?